  <div class="home">
    <img src="Assets/logo/logo.png" id="logo" alt="logo">
    <h1>WELCOME</h1>
    <h1>TO DELANI STUDIO<h1>
    <h5>AMAZING PEOPLE ARE MAKING AMAZING DESIGNS IN A FUN ENVIRONMENT<h5>
